      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a dream to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my trips around town. It looks great and drives even better\u2014perfect for someone who wants a quality car without the 'brand new' price tag. I've taken great care of it, and it's totally ready for its next adventure with you! Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
