    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The powertrain exhibits strong compression and smooth VANOS actuation, delivering a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the cooling system has been refreshed to maintain thermal efficiency under load. The chassis retains its factory-tuned balance with a functional M-variable limited-slip differential and crisp steering rack feedback. While the exterior shows honest signs of use, the mechanical vitals and suspension geometry are sorted, making this a high-performance machine ready for spirited driving.",
